Dialogs.Dialog: Manaka
Did you have your first dream of the year？ I had a dream about a golden rabbit.
Oh, I hope it was a good dream.
Hehe. Say, if you could choose it yourself, what would you like to dream of？
One Fuji, two eagles, three eggplants！
Of course, it would have to be your dream, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
I've never seen it... It would be nice if we could see it together, right？ ...I'm kidding.
...Geez. Then next time, can I visit you in your dreams？
Maybe not only in your dreams... No, it's nothing.
Manaka
Hah... It's so cold, isn't it？
It is！ But, isn't that a good thing, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yeah. But it also gets cold when we're together... right？
I see, then it doesn't change
Do you want to warm each other？
Really？ Then... Can I go a little closer？ Then... hold my hands... a little tighter.
Yes, please. I want you to warm me up... I'm kidding...
Manaka
There's a nice scent near...
This smells is... Plum blossom？ It feels like spring is just around the corner.
Yeah... I wonder from where the scent comes from... Do you want to find it together？
Alright, let's do it！
I think I found your flower already, Manaka
Y... Yeahー！ Ah, didn't you say it too loud？ It's embarrassing...
Then, you're my sun... I'm kidding... Geez, don't make me say that anymore.
Manaka
Ah, Sakura petals...
They are beautiful, but it's a pity they are scattered around.
For sure. I want to see them all the time.
No！ You should only look at me ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
I wish time could stop like this... Haha
Ah！ Yes. Um... Geez, don't say that. You don't want me to look anywhere else？
Hehe, yup. I think I can spend eternity with you. No, rather, I want to spend it with you.
I hope you think so too.
Manaka
...Ah, I'm sorry！ I've been very sleepy lately. I don't have lack off sleep though.
You're cute like that！
I'll help you with that！
I don't believe it, even if it's funny... I won't believe it.
Do you make calls or send mails late every night？
By doing that, I'm happy to be connected to you until I fall asleep.
I yearn for it a little.
Manaka
Ah... did you see it？ It's beautiful.
Ah, it's a rose. This season is for roses.
That's right. The whole month of May is for roses.
Flowers are said to be as beautiful as the care you give them, so people take good care of them.
Like your parents did
They lose to you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Papa and Mama are gardeners？ Or... Are you？ Hehe▼
That again... If you look at me with those eyes, I'll have believe you, right？ Geez...
Manaka
We're past half the year already, right？ Next week, we'll be in July...
You're right, time really flies.
Right. Looking back... All I can see is our memories.
Something like a year's end greeting
This year is all about us！
Yeah. I'm sure it will like that at the end of this year, and the next. Even beyond that, right？ Hehe！
We dyed it with our colors！ I'm kidding... Someday, we'll paint it together, right？
Manaka
There's a lot of time left for winter vacations, isn't it？
Hehe, I don't hate school.
However, summer vacation is over. I wonder what can we do during winter vacation.
I can't wait until winter！
Alright, I'll make a plan for us！
...Hmm. I think you're right. You're eager too？
...Hehe, but what will you do？ That's a way of saying "Let me do it all！ Hehehe！
You'll start now？ ...Yes, winter vacation is short, indeed.
I think if we start right now, we can probably do a lot of things. Do you want to think together？
Manaka
When changing from your winter clothes to your summer clothes, I might have forgotten to put insect repellent...
You mean... Did your clothes get eaten by worms？
Yes, it was Papa's favorite sweater. Mama hand-knitted it...
I bet your mom was surprised too
When I think about your father
Yes, but she was happy about knitting a new one. Thank you for worrying though.
I wonder if it's something men can share with each other.
Someday, I'm sure you'll get the chance to speak with Papa and tell him about it, right？
Manaka
Fuu. It's a little hot, isn't it？
Even though it's only October.
I think summer clothes have failed us...
Actually, I don't think that！
I'll fan you, come closer
Really？ Hmm, then I wasted my time... I'm kidding♪
Yes▼... But if I get too close, it will be hotter rather than cool, right？
Manaka
I have a problem that popped up recently. Why is October also called "Kannazuki"？
Is it a quiz？ Bring it on！
Do you want to know why's it called "Kannazuki"？
...Why don't we check it with the phone？
It's October, you said it before...
Yes, go ahead▼ It's important to find out things you don't understand.
...Hehe, as I expected. But next time I won't lose, okay？
Manaka
I woke up early this morning, so I went to hit the wall for a while...
I see, you do your best in the mornings too.
Hehe, yeah. You know, on my way I was watching the frozen water puddles. They must be cold, right？
I would like to find some ice too！
I bet you liked that, right？
Do you think there's a place with ice left？ Let's make things crunchy with ice♪
...How do you know？ Geez... I don't like it... I'm lying, though.
Manaka
Do you think it is true that the warbler sounds differently depending on the place and age？
I don't think I've ever heard of that...
Is there a different accent in that area, or is there a senior warbler teaching how to sing？
If that's true, don't you think it'll be cute？
We should check it out！
But I think you're better at doing those sounds, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Hehe, right？ Visiting all over Japan, together... I hope we can do it someday▼
That's what I'm talking about... Do you want to go？ C'mon, let's hurry.
Manaka
Did you see the evening news？ I saw a note about a huge rabbit.
How big？
Um... A man picked it up, and it reached from the tip of his foot to his knee.
And it's weight was maybe... about half of mine？
Ah, it sounds like it was so fluffy！
I think I should just hug you！
Hehehe, right？
Hey, can we go to the zoo next time？ I want to visit to the petting corner▼
Eh！ Um... Right here...？ ...Geez, no！
Manaka
Ah, a cat.
Where？
Look, over there. Two of them are snuggling up and grooming. It's so cute...
I want to pet them
We won't lose to them！
Hmm, if you get in the way, you'll be kicked by a horse. Well, maybe not a horse, but a cat, right？ Hehehe！
Geez, I'm not trying to compete with them... But I agree. We should snug a lot more... Right？
Manaka
The dog we saw earlier...
Yes, it was cute！ With its round eyes, swinging its tail！ I wanted to hug it！
Umm... I mean... Right？
Please don't worry.
But, if you don't take care of me, I might start to feel a little lonely... I'm kidding.
...As a punishment, how about hugging me？ We have a lot of things to do today.
Manaka
Do you know what happened the other day？ I was invited by the basketball club advisor to join.
Huh！？ You didn't accept, did you？
...Who knows？
Then I'll go with you！
You must be in the tennis club！
Hehe, going together？ It's okay, I won't leave. Let's do our best together in the tennis club, okay？
...Can you say tell me why？ Then I'll think about it... I'm kidding.
Manaka will never leave you▼ Hehe！
Manaka
Have you seen Suzuki sensei's mobile phone？
His phone？ No, but why？
The standby screen is the picture of his child. It looks like he takes a lot of photos of his son.
I think he goes "dere" sometimes！
I'll do the same someday, I'm sure...
I guess it's really cute. Would you like me to ask him to show it to us next time？ Hehe！
Do you think that'll happen？
Before that, can you fill your phone with my photos？ I'm kidding！
Manaka
There's a rumor about the length of the skirt of our uniforms becoming longer in the future, but... do you think it's true？
Seriously！？
...Hmm？ Do you think that's bad？
Umm... No, not much. Maybe？
No, it suits you well ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Really now？ Geez, your eyes tell me otherwise. Pervert.
...Hehe！ You're making a face like you've said something good.
From cute to unquestioned▼ I'm kidding.
Manaka
I have a friend who calls his father by his name... Is that natural？
Hmm, I wonder about it. It seems it's becoming a common thing.
I wonder about that... If I did that, I might be disowned.
Why don't you try it here with me？
If it happens, come live with me！
Eh, uh... I won't do it！ Geez, if you tell me that, I won't do it.
..."It's a joke", I don't need to hear that... Geez.
Manaka
Is my way of speaking strange？
Hmmー, I don't think so. Why do you ask？
I was told that the way I say some words are not modern. How modern should I speak？
Something like saying "srly"？
I want you to stay that way！
Did you hear that word before？ “Serious” is "Really”, isn't it？... Srly？ Hmm...
...Yes, I understand▼ But, I was just curious...
Hey, can you tell me more about it next time？ How about doing it when studying together？
Manaka
Did you know there's a guy who plays in a band in my class？ I was asked to play the keyboard with them...
Mmm, what kind of band？
A rock band. But I wonder if it's okay to do some research before.
I didn't know you were so intense about music, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
You don't need to do that too！
Geez, what are you imagining？ It's nothing that violent！
...But, would you like to see me in one？
I see... I don't know much about rock. If you have a recommended rock band, let me know.
Manaka
The other day, I tried to play a difficult piano piece for the first time in a long time.
Oh, how was it？
It was alright. I have to practice more at home.
I would like to see you practice
I want to hear it too！
...No. Because I would be saying every time "Don't look at me like that".
So I wish to practice some more before, okay？
Really？... I absolutely love you...
Manaka
Last night, I watched Cinderella after a long time.
The Anime？ On DVD？
Yes, that was the one. It was wonderful.
I also want to see it...
▲高嶺＊＊▲... You know you might look...
Then, do you want to watch it together in my room next time？ Hehe, I'm looking forward to it.
Childish... Maybe. But I might like it more now, because I met my real prince▼
Manaka
I wonder if cleaning will bring something good to me...
I think you're getting addicted to that, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Geez... Do you think so？
It's something only I can tell, I think
I think that's something cute
You know me better than myself, don't you？... Hehe, that's funny.
That's not an answer... Why do you always say that？ Geez...
Manaka
I always thought that my sleep posture isn't that bad, don't you think？
Hmm？ Did something happen？
Yeah, I fell out of my bed last night. It's been a while since I was so scared... so I laughed.
Did you fall head-first？
I wanted to see you fall！
Hehe, yes, it used to happen when I was little. I wonder why I was moving out so much？
Then, next time... Can't you be more delicate？ ... Idiot.
Manaka
Hey, I have a question.
Yes, go ahead！
Hehe！ I was wondering, what kind of people your friends are like？
Are you interested in them？
No, I won't introduce you to them！
It's no good then. Your girlfriend wants to know everything about you. I'm kidding.
Geez, that's not the case... Hey, did you get jealous perhaps？ That's so cute▼
Manaka
Is blogging interesting？
Some people find it interesting. Are you thinking about doing it？
Hmm... I haven't decided yet. You know, there are many people doing it.
Shall we do a love diary？
Let's do something crazy！
Eh... Can there be something like that？... Then, can we not do it？ I want to keep them in secret... I'm kidding.
...I can't be more crazy than you. Don't do anything weird. Tsk！ Hehe！
Manaka
I sometimes can't see it...
Hmm？ What do you mean？
How does a person use two mobile phones at once？ How would you use them？
Private and for work！
I would use both for you ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Hehe, what's with that answer. But, they could be used that way, I see...
You mean... Sending mails while calling me. Hehe, it might be interesting.
Manaka
What would you think if I learned karate and aikido？
Eh, why those？
I saw them in the news last night. It was about a junior high school girl, but I wanted to try it.
Do you have a gi, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...？
I will protect you ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
What did you imagine？ Do you think there are any cute Keikogi's to wear？
Thank you. But... I also want to protect you. That said, it's okay to try, right？
Manaka
Say, what would you do if we suddenly couldn't see each other？
If we can't see each other, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yes, I had that dream last night... I was so sad...
I will do anything for you！
I won't let that happen
...Geez. If I was told that, it would make me feel stupid... Thank you...
Really？ ...You won't leave me and go away？ Promise me.
Manaka
There are people who are good at taking photos with a phone, right？
I'm here！ I can make photos look good.
How can I be able to take shoots like that？ I want to know some tips.
Move like this, and strike a pose
You are already good enough, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Something like this？ How about this？ Geez, don't stay silent, say something will you？ I'm embarrassed.
That's not helpful at all. Don't please me like that, I want to spoil you now...
Manaka
Hey, is there something you're hiding from me？
Hiding something！？ I have nothing like that！
To say it so quickly, isn't it suspicious？ I won't be angry, can you be honest with me？
Hidden equals love, right？
I'll say I love you most！
Hmm, is that your reason？ I'm kidding. But not too much, right？ Otherwise, I'll be jealous.
Why hide it？ Even if you tell me that every day, I...
Can you say it again？ ...This time, seriously. C'mon, hurry▼
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
Huh？ What's wrong？
Did I do something？
I'm sorry, it's nothing. I just wanted to say your name▼
Yay, you understood▼ Well, I just wanted you to say my name.
Manaka
Have you ever wondered from where your name comes from, ▲主人公＊▲？
Umm, now that you ask...
I haven't bothered investigating
I've heard it from my parents
Really？ Is it because you're a boy...？
Hehe, did you now？ Is that a road everyone goes through once？
Can you say my name please, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
Huh？ Umm... ▲主人公＊▲.
Yeah, I'm so happy！
Hehe, if you like that, I'll do it as much as you want. ▲主人公＊▲.
Geez, what kind of game is that, ▲主人公＊▲？ Hehe！
